title: Grateful Dead Live at Shoreline Amphitheatre on 1993-08-27
description:
Set 1

Mississippi Half Step, Minglewood Blues, Lazy River Road, Broken Arrow, Eternity, Loose Lucy, Johnny B. Goode

Set 2

Iko Iko, Wave To The Wind, Playin' In The Band-> Uncle John's Band, Corinna, Drums-> Jam-> I Need A Miracle, The Days Between-> Throwing Stones-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: I Fought The Law
